OL,5, Almost a third of university courses   
OL,6, are still combining face-to-face       
OL,7, teaching with online learning in       
OL,8, 2022-23, data gathered by the BBC      
OL,9, suggests.                              
OL,11,FData from 50 of the 160 universities   
OL,12,Fsurveyed shows 28% of courses are being
OL,13,Ftaught in a hybrid way, compared with  
OL,14,F4.1% in 2018-19 before the pandemic.   
OL,16,FOne student said he feels like he is   
OL,17,Fpaying thousands of pounds per year for
OL,18,Fa "glorified streaming service".       
OL,20,FBut an official says many students     
OL,21,Fappreciate the flexibility and freedom.
